title: Lizzy Caplan
itunes:title: Lizzy Caplan
itunes:subtitle: LIZZY CAPLAN (Freaks and Geeks, Mean Girls, Cloverfield, Masters of Sex) joins Anna to discuss living abroad, friend dates, a fateful bus advertisement, marriage, TV sex and more. Anna and Lizzy then give Unqualified advice to callers Elizabeth and Melani
description:
In this episode...

- Living abroad
- Friend dates
- Diminishing brain cells
- A cup of tea
- Professional vs. personal identity
- The California trucker hat
- Marriage
- Ticks vs. aliens
- Chad talks with Lizzy
- How Lizzy got her man
- A song and dance
- TV sex vs. porn
- Advice to callers Elizabeth and Melanie
